One way to use the network tools in Zephyr
------------------------------------------

# Go to Zephyr sources and configure submodules
$ cd $ZEPHYR_BASE
$ git submodule add --name 'net/ip/tools' git://git-amr-4.devtools.intel.com/zephyr_os_net_tools-tools.git net/ip/tools

# Update the net tools
$ git submodule update --init --recursive
